mes for fun, the folks I group with play games for fun, I spent 6 hours happily in BoT last night casting mainly shock of magic doing very respectable damage on every pull, never went out of mana tho I was a little lower than if I'd been using just draughts) is there a problem here? Really some folks need to remember this is a game and enjoy the fun things about it.<br>
